                        <p><strong>TC: What advice would you offer students who similarly have a question they’d like to get answered?</strong></p>
<p><strong>AB</strong>: Focus on your studies first, that’s what I always do. But there’s always something interesting if you keep your eyes open and if you are not afraid to question what you see or what you hear. One should not shy away from questioning authority. And this shows through in the way that I teach my classes.</p>
<!--EndFragment-->
